description: Bong AB engages in the provision of specialty packaging and envelope products in Europe. The company is headquartered in Kristianstad, Skane and currently employs 1,200 full-time employees.  The company is engaged in the development, manufacture and marketing of envelopes and specialty packaging, gift wrapping, paper bags, packaging equipment , as well as offers services, such as overprinting. The firm markets its specialty packaging under the ProPac brand. Additionally, the Company offers a non-woven high-density polyethylene packaging material, Tyvek. The firm has offices in 21 European countries, including Sweden, Norway, Denmark, Finland and Germany, among others. As of December 31, 2013, the Company had two wholly owned subsidiaries, namely Bong International AB domiciled in Sweden and Bong GmbH domiciled in Germany.
